v1.5.2
	* Create more config options, e. g. mouse buttons and keyboard keys.
	* Repaint ruling and onion layers after erasing.
v1.5.1
	* Create config for most settings, overwriteable by user.
	* Optional memory usage display.
v1.5
	* Support for any screen size.
v1.4
	* Added ruling and graph paper.
	* Added splash screen for help.
v1.3.1
	* Fixed sorting of notebooks.
v1.3
	* Added eraser on right click.
	- Sorting notebooks in the selection window.
v1.2.2
	* Multiple layers in onion mode.
	- Added window icon in notebook view too.
v1.2.1
	* Using git describe version number.
v1.2
	* Added onion layer mode.
v1.1.1
	* Added "make install" target.
v1.1
	* Added German localization.
	* Added scroll panels for touch only devices.
	* Using a config file.
	- Added -v flag to activate log messages.
	- Added logo to main window.
	- Added simple man page.
	- Deleting the temporary files after the programs exists.
	- Disallowing to resize the window.
	- Fixed null pointer exception when clicking cancel on new dialog.
	- Fixed temp file permissions.
v1.0.1
	* Added desktop entry.
	* Added launcher script
	* Added logo for the program.
v1.0
	* Do not close application after closing notebook.
	* Drastically simplified file structure, tests are still buggy.
	* Opening notebook on double click.
	* Saving all notebooks that are opened when closing the opening dialog.
	- Added version flag to CLI.
	- Bug fix blank page reloading error.
	- Fixed case where going back and forth faster than WriteoutThread could handle writing.
v0.3
	* Added default directory option.
	* Added delete function.
	* Added help message.
	* Added more keys to control program.
	* Only draw with primary mouse button.
	- Ask user when the default directory is not valid any more.
	- Display page count in overview.
v0.2.1
	* Added option to write out loading and writing.
v0.2
	* Added "scribble" mode.
	* Added ability to paint a single dot.
	* Added basic lines for the background.
	* Added basic notebook selection window.
	* Added full screen support.
	* Added support for notebooks in folders.
	* Centering all new windows.
	* Going to last page in notebook after opening it.
	* Loading pictures in right order.
	- Added meaningful error messages.
	- Added memory usage display.
	- Added scroll pane around list.
	- Added total page number to display.
	- Added touched/unsaved differentiation.
	- Do not save empty pictures.
	- Fancy name in the window title.
	- Only using full screen when the display is the same size.
	- Open notebook after creation.
	- Put the swapping into a separate thread.
	- Swapping in backwards direction as well.
	- Using zero padding in filename for the date.
v0.1
